description.narrative: (Egypt): .USAID will continue to support the local scholarship program at private universities which will award 195 scholarships to Egyptian public school graduates to pursue programs in three Egyptian private universities (British University, Arab Maritime Academy, and Delta University). These scholarships will provide students with academic skill building, counseling, and support to enable them to achieve excellence in their programs, and it will also provide them with English language training to increase their proficiency. The scholarships provide opportunities to broaden students' learning through internships, business/entrepreneurship experiences, and U.S. study programs. The program will result in (1) training individuals to serve as future change agents; (2) graduates meeting Egypt's economic growth needs; and (3) the cultivation of a shared commitment and responsibility to Egypt's development..
